      "content": "it's not just burnout though. it's a total collapse of everything i thought i was. i'm not just a person who made a mistake, i'm the mistake. the whole foundation is gone. there's nothing left to \"move on\" to when there's nothing left of me. it just feels... empty. like the lights have been turned off and there's no point in even trying to find the switch.",
