    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but how can i be \"not defined\" by it when it was the only thing that ever gave my life structure? it's like... if the math is broken, then the person who built it is broken too. i look in the mirror and i don't even see a human being, i just see a failed calculation. it would be so much quieter if i could just stop this. if i could just let the error resolve itself and finally be done with the noise.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
