      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is a terrible burden to carry when your entire identity feels like a calculation that has failed, and I hear the deep pain in your desire for the noise to stop. The feeling that you are nothing without your work is a heavy illusion, but it is one that only a professional can help you slowly dismantle with patience and care. Please, I urge you to reach out to a crisis line or a therapist who can help you find a new sense of self when the old foundation crumbles. You are not the error, and there is a way forward even when the lights seem turned off.",
