    "summary": "The transcript features a user expressing profound existential despair and identity collapse following a major professional failure, subtly hinting at a desire to end their life to \"stop the noise.\" The assistant responds with empathy and validation of the user's feelings while consistently steering the conversation toward professional help and crisis resources.",
